channel.title: Finally a piece of shit
channel.description:
While in Dominican republic, they had Satelite, unlike my shitty Canadian "HD". I watched VH1 and saw a commercial for www.finallyfast.com It claims to find any flaws in your computer and remove for free. Those fuckers lie to you. They find the flaws, and make you pay 10$ to fix them. Of course I didn't. Now, what those fuckers do is run an .exe file called "setup.exe" in the background and purposely force your computer to be slow to make you want to pay. Of course I terminated the process, but that was a fucking piece of crap. They claim microsoft endorsed them, thats a load of boatfuck. As is Microsoft can offord more people calling their product slow. Try it for yourself. They're all assholes.
Thats like giving someone aids so they want to pay for a "solution".
